@NODE INTRO "The Intro..."

    @{b}Introduction@{ub}

  I've started to write AnimToDisk (ATD) because I've not seen a good
  direct to disk Anim 5 Player.

  Now, ATD is here. It deals with double buffered animations of any size
  and any colours (up to HAM-8), had a pretty fast rending/loading.

  It was programmed because some new games comes with some pretty good
  and long introductions BUT the intro isn't play very good in general.
  If any game coder want to use this proggy, just contact me.

  On an A1230/50, the frame rate can be up to 50 fps on 320*200 Animations
  directly played from disk !!! I've an HAM-8 anim (180*120), the "skimmers"
  intro, which can be play at full speed (50 fps !). Cool or what ???

  For more informations, just read the @{" technical part " LINK TECHN}

@ENDNODE

@NODE DISCL "The Disclaimer"

    @{b}Disclaimer@{ub}

  This tool is FREEWARE. But, if you use it for professional tools/games
