@NODE FEATU

    @{b}Features@{ub}

        * Support Standard IFF-Anim 5 Animations
        * Very Fast PlayBack DIRECT FROM DISK
        * Each animations part can be have their own palette,
          but Multipalette animations AREN'T SUPPORTED !
          The Palette is changed in REAL Time without any bugs ! :-)
          Just try it.
        * Timer support (You can playback at your desirated rate)
        * Different check to prevent crash in low memory situation.
        * PERFECT Playback (no frames skipped, no interuption during
          loading...)

@ENDNODE

